<h2 class="line">Summary</h2>

<p>We reviewed $707,000 of the Community Services Block Grant program Recovery Act funds that Pennsylvania's Department of Community and Economic Development (State agency) claimed on behalf of Community Action Program of Lancaster County (Lancaster) and determined that the State agency claimed $2,800 in unallowable entertainment costs for Lancaster.  </p>



